2023-06-03  [Ricardo Mones] 4.1.1-62-g7c1ea64fe

	* src/plugins/fancy/fancy_viewer.c		
		Fix error creation and warning  The error won't be created if the
		GQuark is 0, only a warning is emitted and NULL is returned. See:
		https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/glib/-/blob/main/glib/gerror.c#L792

