		configuring the tags, or modifying the tags of the selected
		message(s); display or don't display the label in the window,
		depending on the same; improve the English usage; make the 'add'
		button sensitive, so we don't need the 'tag not set' warning if
		someone presses Add without setting the tag name; only show the
		vertidal scrollbar when needed; lots of renaming, e.g. not
		'apply_window' but 'tags_window'

