2021-09-09  [Jonathan Boeing] 4.0.0-145-g0c7308ca2

	* src/editaddress.c		
		Fix crash in address book edit person details  Bug 4534 'Address book
		causing claws to terminate unexpectedly'  Clearing the list store
		triggers a cursor-changed signal, leading to a potential crash with a
		use-after-free

