2021-09-08  [wwp] 4.0.0-130-gd4e2645d8

	* src/textview.c		
		Allow zooming in/out a message body text view. Zoom level is applied
		to any further message viewed, and reset at next start-up. Only
		applies to text font. Zoom is changed by using CTRL+mouse wheel
		up/down, or with text view's right-click menu.

2021-09-08  [wwp] 3.18.0-82-gf577e0432

	* src/textview.c		
		Allow zooming in/out a message body text view. Zoom level is applied
		to any further message viewed, and reset at next start-up. Only
		applies to text font. Zoom is changed by using CTRL+mouse wheel
		up/down, or with text view's right-click menu.

