2021-07-12  [paul] 3.18.0-3-g4b04819b9

	* src/imap.c		
		move OAuth2 to last place in auto auth selection  IMAP: when using
		'automatic' auth type, if the server offers LOGIN, GSSAPI or
		plaintext in addition to OAUTH2, yet OAUTH2 is unconfigured,
		authentication will fail. This broke previously working config

2021-07-12  [paul] 4.0.0-4-g9c2585c58

	* src/imap.c		
		move OAuth2 to last place in auto auth selection  IMAP: when using
		'automatic' auth type, if the server offers LOGIN, GSSAPI or
		plaintext in addition to OAUTH2, yet OAUTH2 is unconfigured,
		authentication will fail. This broke previously working config

