2020-12-27  [Michael Rasmussen] 3.99.0-17-g959585854

	* src/plugins/fancy/fancy_viewer.c		
		Fix bug #4425: Open link in external browser. Original patch by
		Orivej Desh. Added fix for crash on right-click on links 

2020-12-23  [paul] 3.99.0-16-gf43e00645

	* AUTHORS
	* src/gtk/authors.h		
		update contributors list

2020-12-16  [Orivej Desh] 3.99.0-15-g6eb5afe08

	* src/plugins/fancy/fancy_viewer.c
	* src/plugins/fancy/fancy_viewer.h		
		Disable remote content by using a void proxy 
		enable-dns-prefetching=0 has stopped blocking remote content after
		the switch to webkit2gtk. Disabling it with a false proxy works. 
		Setting proxy to "" works well with libsoup-backed webkit2gtk since
		it prevents any connection attempts. If libcurl-backed webkit2gtk
		won't like it, it may be replaced by "http://127.0.0.9:9" (with 9
		being reserved for the discard service, and 127.0.0.9 being more
		greppable than 127.0.0.1). 

