		Restore original "special case" comment in GtkCMCLists draw_rows()

2019-03-24  [Andrej Kacian] 3.16.0-621-g5e93424f7

	* src/gtk/gtkcmclist.c		
		Finally fix the wonky GtkCMCList redraw when scrolling it 
		draw_rows() expects area rectangle in coordinates relative to
		clist_window, but gtk_cmclist_draw() was passing it a rectangle in
		coordinates relative to the GdkWindow of the entire widget.

