2019-01-13  [Andrej Kacian] 3.16.0-594-g095a3ea40

	* src/folderview.c		
		Fix alignment on folderview title button icons  This also fixes some
		GTK runtime warnings at startup

2019-01-13  [Andrej Kacian] 3.16.0-593-gc6b9d4745

	* src/gtk/gtkcmclist.c		
		In GtkCMCList, do not try to allocate title button sizes if the
		widget is not ready  This fixes fixes several GTK runtime warnings
		displayed on startup and when switching between layouts. Plus, saves
		some CPU cycles, obviously.

2019-01-13  [Andrej Kacian] 3.16.0-592-g4b9adc862

	* src/image_viewer.c		
		Fix click-to-resize in image viewer  GtkScrolledWindow does not seem
		to intercept button-press-event when pointer is on its content, and
		GtkImage does not have GdkWindow of its own, so it can't accept
		events. We add a GtkEventBox around the image to work around this.

2019-01-12  [Andrej Kacian] 3.16.0-591-g3833e1f72

	* src/image_viewer.c		
		Fix image viewer resizing  For some reason, GTK3's GtkImage does not
		update its size when new contents get set to it. We have to force it
		by calling gtk_widget_size_allocate() on its parent container.

