		Restore prefswindow's remembered size correctly.

2018-10-04  [Andrej Kacian] 3.16.0-373-gf71ca14f9

	* src/folderview.c
	* src/mainwindow.c
	* src/summaryview.c		
		Make main mainwindow components' sizing slightly more sane. 
		gtk_widget_set_size_request() is setting minimal widget size now, so
		we can't use it for restoring remembered component sizes anymore,
		since then they can't be made any smaller than the remembered size
		anymore.

