2017-02-25  [Andrej Kacian] 3.14.1-202-ga0cd16371

	* src/plugins/rssyl/opml_import.c
	* src/plugins/rssyl/rssyl.c
	* src/plugins/rssyl/rssyl_cb_menu.c
